  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "In a large bowl whisk together orange juice, olive oil, smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper",
    "Add the chicken to the bowl and marinate for at least 30 minutes",
    "Thread the marinated chicken, cherry tomatoes, and red onion onto skewers",
    "Grill the kebabs for 10-12 minutes or until the chicken is cooked through",
    "Let the kebabs rest for 5 minutes before serving",
    "Serve the kebabs hot with your favorite sides",
    "Store any leftovers in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to 3 days"
  ],
